    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><em>A shimmering shield forms around one of your arms, allowing you to block incoming attacks.</em></p><p><strong>Buff:</strong></p><p>You cast this spell to block an incoming attack.</p><p>If you are holding a shield, you cannot gain the benefits of your shield and this spell at the same time.</p><ul><li><p>You have a +3* bonus to AC for 1 round, including against the triggering attack, and you take no damage from magic missile.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> The bonus to AC increases by 1 for each spell level above 1st, to a maximum of +5 to AC.</p></div>",
            "chat": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><strong>Buff:</strong></p><p>You cast this spell to block an incoming attack.</p><p>If you are holding a shield, you cannot gain the benefits of your shield and this spell at the same time.</p><ul><li><p>You have a +3* bonus to AC for 1 round, including against the triggering attack, and you take no damage from magic missile.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> The bonus to AC increases by 1 for each spell level above 1st, to a maximum of +5 to AC.</p></div>"
